841845299.text: "p21 WAF1 and/or p16 INK4A both inhibit the activity of cyclin dependent protein kinases (CDKs) that phosphorylate and inactivate the Retinoblastoma protein (Rb), leading to accumulation of the hypo phosphorylated, active form of Rb that mediates cell-cycle arrest and other phenotypes of senescence."
